name: Pre-Lit Twig Tree, Black
description: This sparkly black twig tree provides a great background for your Halloween decorations or can be used at Christmas for a unique and modern decorative effect along with your baubles.

name: Festive Fir Unlit Christmas Tree
description: Our Festive Fir offers you excellent value for money. Its classic conical shape has realistic green tips to show off your decorations.

description: Tiny, warm white LEDs form delicate clusters, on silver wire and are battery-operated, making them easy and versatile to use. The only limit is your imagination. Indoor use only.

description: These beautifully-finished robin design Christmas crackers will make for a wonderful addition to any table. Finished with luxurious satin ribbon.

description: The back rest is made from breathable mesh and we've upholstered the seat in a soft fabric.

description: Designed for short periods at your desk and light computer use, our Reid office chair is height-adjustable to suit each user. Its tub shape incorporates armrests and its faux leather upholstery means it's easy to wipe clean.

description: Well-proportioned for your home office, the Franklin desk is made from wood and designed with marquetry techniques to create a tactile, geometric facade.

name: Abacus Filing Desk, FSC-Certified
description: This simple, roomy desk with its built-in set of drawers offers useful storage space and a convenient place to work.

name: Loft 2 Drawer Filing Cabinet, Grey/White
description: Tuck this practical filing cabinet under our coordinating Loft desk to complete your home office set up.

name: Quick-Heating Round Inflatable Hot Tub with Filter Pack, Chemicals & Cover Bundle, 6 Person
description: This six-person hot tub comes with two filter cartridges and a chemical starter kit with everything you need to keep your hot tub clean.

name: 4 Burner Gas BBQ, Silver/Black
description: The 4-burner gas barbecue is perfect for catering for several people when cooking outdoors.
